ght-volume series, includes a complete textual apparatus as well as a historical introduction and full critical and explanatory annotation.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aClothing and dressvFiction. 0aConduct of lifevFiction. 0aPhilosophersvFiction. 4aBritain. 4aEuropean history. 4ahistory. 4apublic. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / English, Irish, Scottish, Welsh.2bisacsh1 aEngel, Mark, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt40uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520353985?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520353985423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520353985/original  aEBA_EMB  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles